At this point, one should note that strictly speaking the offset is only an approximate measure of the efficiency of electron escape from PSI to the electrolyte (in all the samples under study) and may underestimate this efficiency in all the samples under study. This statement may be justified in the following way. Equation 2 may be rewritten in the form:4koutkav=constA1+A2,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
